{"tid":1798837,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"D社爆出Red Velvet Wendy從2.5m墜落受傷的詳情：連標記貼紙也沒有！","createTime":"2019-12-26T13:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T03:11:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3a349cf65bb6faf539d39fb3102b19176325ba","tid":1798837,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"根據Dispatch的報導，Wendy在25日上午11點第一輪彩排，進行了電影《阿拉丁》OST《Speechless》的音響測試。 「Wendy的舞台動線很簡單，就是經過隧道後走下階梯。但是隧道狹窄黑暗，連常見的螢光標記貼紙都沒有。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「Wendy按照臺本登上了2層的隧道，配合歌曲準備從階梯下來，但是這時升降式階梯沒有升上來，就在這一瞬間失去重心墜落。」事故發生後，現場一片混亂，Wendy被送上急救車送去急救室，Red Velvet成員聽到消息受到衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n相關人士還表示：「Wendy墜落事故發生後，多個組合也是要登上2層隧道，在惶恐不安之中進行了表演。」<br />\n<br />\n此次事故導致Wendy至少需要6周的治療，右側骨盆和手腕骨折，右側顴骨出現裂傷，全身多處跌傷，需要數月才能恢復。"},{"pid":"67a31a5bacca32a795012ce82bce037c1ea46c0a","tid":1798837,"uid":21526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d4bbed40274f4ba12152e310b34472fe32ccb7","tid":1798837,"uid":16659,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6d707b0c4d575b594161f0688ef94110/4feb5ed34f2dae4a-13/s400x600/e406d622112a6260ecead3eda11a588dcb1d1dc8.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6d707b0c4d575b594161f0688ef94110%2F4feb5ed34f2dae4a-13%2Fs400x600%2Fe406d622112a6260ecead3eda11a588dcb1d1dc8.gifv&h=d84bae5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/01f7e6509ad2a29e336e613cb04fabf3/4feb5ed34f2dae4a-8c/s400x600/82e2ebe4af30cd2261f6527c3c23e80f2c41cc3c.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F01f7e6509ad2a29e336e613cb04fabf3%2F4feb5ed34f2dae4a-8c%2Fs400x600%2F82e2ebe4af30cd2261f6527c3c23e80f2c41cc3c.gifv&h=41e75112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/473414896d8d3